'''提康德羅加堡戰'''（'''Battle of Ticonderoga'''<ref>{{cite book |author=Loescher B. G. |title= Genesis, Rogers Rangers: The First Green Berets, The Corps & The Revivals, April 6, 1758-December 24, 1783 (A heritage classic) |year= 2007 |publisher= Heritage Books |isbn= 0788415751| page= 3 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author= Reid S. |title= Quebec 1759: The Battle That Won Canada (Campaign) |url= https://archive.org/details/quebecbattlethat00reid |year= 2003 |publisher= Osprey Publishing |isbn= 1855326051 |page= [https://archive.org/details/quebecbattlethat00reid/page/n9 9] }}</ref>），	指[[法國-印第安人戰爭|法國-印第安人戰爭]]期間，1759年7月26日及27日一場輕微的戰術對抗，地點在鐘琴砲台（Fort Carillon，後改稱 Fort Ticonderoga，即提康德羅加砲台<ref>{{cite book |author= Nester W. R. |title= The Epic Battles for Ticonderoga, 1758 |year= 2008 |publisher= State University of New York Press |isbn= 079147321X |page= 239 }}</ref>）。[[杰弗里‧阿默斯特|杰弗里‧阿默斯特]]將軍（General Sir Jeffrey Amherst）指揮，[[英國|英國]]軍事武力11000多人，移動火砲到高地，俯瞰砲台。準將[[弗朗索瓦-夏爾·德·布拉馬克|弗朗索瓦-夏爾·德·布拉馬克]]<ref>{{cite book |author= Chartrand R. |title= Ticonderoga 1758: Montcalm's victory against all odds (Campaign) |url= https://archive.org/details/ticonderogamontc00char |year=  2000 |publisher= Osprey Publishing |isbn= 1841760935 |page= [https://archive.org/details/ticonderogamontc00char/page/n21 21] }}</ref>指揮，撤防400個法國人守衛砲台。

